@startuml
!theme plain

title AD06 - Generate Reports

|User|
start
:Select "Generate Reports";
:Select Report Type
(Production Summary / Machine Utilization / Operator Performance);
:Set Date Range / Filter;
:Click Generate;

|System|
:Validate Filter;
if (Valid Filter?) then (yes)
  :Fetch Production Data;
  :Aggregate and Process Data;
  :Generate Report Object;
  if (Export Format == PDF?) then (yes)
    :Export to PDF;
  elseif (Export Format == CSV?) then (yes)
    :Export to CSV;
  else (Preview)
    :Show Preview;
  endif
  :Save / Download Report;
else (no)
  :Show Validation Error;
endif

|User|
stop

@enduml